title: Media Alert: AutoConnect 2015
text:
FBTAuto
NASHVILLE, Tenn. , Oct. 14,
WHAT:
AUTOCONNECT 2015 CONFERENCE
AutoConnect was formed to serve the business, finance, and government environment in a way that strengthens the infrastructure and complements the considerable investment made by automotive manufacturing companies. AutoConnect provides a focal point that works to facilitate growth and continued investment in the Southern U.S. AutoConnect 2015 is presented by the FBT automotive industry practice team, FBTAuto.
WHO:
AutoConnect 2015 brings together original equipment manufacturers (OEMs), suppliers, investors, bankers and others to network on global industry issues.
For a list of presenters go to: www.fbtautoconnect.com/presenters.html
Click on their names for background information.
For the schedule, go to: www.fbtautoconnect.com/schedule.html
WHEN:
AutoConnect 2015 will be held tomorrow, October 15 th , registration from 7:30 – 8:00 a.m. Sen. Bob Corker kicks things off with Opening Remarks at 8:00 a.m.
WHERE:
At the Music City Center located at 201, 5 th Ave., South in downtown Nashville.
HOW:
Media are invited to register on site and attend open panels.
For more information visit: www.fbtautoconnect.com
Contact: Gordon Cole
248.207.0525
gcole@p2rassociates.com
